  <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-132cbc5c-7e1a-4c74-9a34-4ab00de4bde4\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-ebc99843-a7e9-4389-8fb5-a6229a5d9994\">그러나.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-82e398bc-b1af-450c-995b-9b2b3e79cdda\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-968e650e-6a15-47ac-ada4-42427a43f4f2\">달리기 뒷날 아침에 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-70c35c75-5c34-4be2-892b-57dfc582c886\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-7024be53-5441-4e14-9428-0038bf991101\">걷기 힘들 정도의 무릎 통증에 시달렸네요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6cce4f69-a014-41c9-a8ac-dc3ca9c7c96f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-82d5f001-785e-4592-936b-dbe9068ac56c\">급하게 침치료 및 봉침치료하고  스트레칭과 아이스팩, 그리고 안정휴식을 통해</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-40dc8dba-09a1-4e6e-a87e-fffedb9797c7\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-b90ddcf9-3152-49f9-96be-0f6c17c430ca\">완화되더니 오후즈음엔 걸을만해지더군요. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f415d13a-ee5d-4a05-a083-547a60da4784\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-023adc50-1b61-410e-a96a-f254f34230e6\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-10738e59-6d2f-4273-b2a4-e4ba894493f6\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-2868928f-fda1-4be5-ad03-31fb4357691a\">무릎은 2-3일 불안한 상태로 유지되다가</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b265c75d-9fb2-4e1a-bb10-19fd929f7930\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-67fba408-3b7d-4524-9a99-0d180f829057\">4-5일 지나니 &#x27;이젠 괜찮은가&#x27; 싶을 정도로 회복되었습니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d0580947-f03f-47c0-9379-0fba5a27b103\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-68529f89-5418-400c-8818-38d9c0b98d9c\">그래도 운동손상이 회복될 시간이 필요하니까 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3807fb5f-709f-4969-ab3f-cbab65f6cee0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-112b56b7-d4da-4c57-af26-82abfff225dc\">참고 참다가, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d2ec78b-6562-4351-896e-1be772f5b2fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-56482bb7-45f5-419f-a2f5-b0e1d87c9736\">어제 다시 달리기에 도전합니다. </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-bce8299b-7d16-432c-8f7a-34b0abc57a20\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-c9c2cfd7-6d1f-4d12-8fa0-e55eb80f63fa\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-ff22a48d-f4ec-46a1-a600-19738ee80e2e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-   \" id=\"SE-85eab97f-a977-4d22-bd2a-4eeb97d83814\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-a39f9c5b-f550-40a7-9940-99d50754c91e\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-a